  "source": "Derived via Hidden Structure from langchain-oss-python. Source observation: Extracted 2026-05-25 from LangChain and LangGraph public repository manifests plus current LangChain docs. Edge convention: 'X depends on Y' = X imports, requires, or declares Y as an optional integration. Pinned to commit 33875fde2acf6ffb717915a895638274a6098ec2. langgraph companion-repo edges are not clone-grounded (langgraph not cloned in research/repos/); they are downgraded to docs-tier and pinned to langgraph repo commit add269632bb32c57f3252b7a7006c8115b579fb4 (tag 1.2.2).",
  "narrative": {
    "mode": "walkthrough",
    "steps": [
